rator.','Enter your <a href="https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1" target="_blank">criticalcss.com</a> API key above. The key is revalidated every time a new job is sent to it.<br />To obtain your API key, go to <a href="https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1" target="_blank">criticalcss.com</a> > Account > API Keys.<br />Requests to generate a critical CSS via the API are priced at £5 per domain per month.<br /><strong>Not sure yet? With the <a href="https://criticalcss.com/faq/?aff=1#trial" target="_blank">30 day money back guarantee</a>, you have nothing to lose!</strong>'=>'Enter your <a href="https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1" target="_blank">criticalcss.com</a> API key above. The key is revalidated every time a new job is sent to it.<br />To obtain your API key, go to <a href="https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1" target="_blank">criticalcss.com</a> > Account > API Keys.<br />Requests to generate a critical CSS via the API are priced at £5 per domain per month.<br /><strong>Not sure yet? With the <a href="https://criticalcss.com/faq/?aff=1#trial" target="_blank">30 day money back guarantee</a>, you have nothing to lose!</strong>','Could not create the required directory. Make sure the webserver can write to the wp-content/uploads directory.'=>'Could not create the required directory. Make sure the webserver can write to the wp-content/uploads directory.','Critical CSS'=>'Critical CSS','Enable site configuration?'=>'Enable site configuration?','Enable Autoptimize configuration per site.'=>'Enable Autoptimize configuration per site.','Autoptimize is enabled and configured on a WordPress network level. Please contact your network administrator if you need Autoptimize settings changed.'=>'Autoptimize is enabled and configured on a WordPress network level. Please contact your network administrator if you need Autoptimize settings changed.','Important: excluded non-minified files are still minified by Autoptimize unless that 